<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhtimine </eesti>
<inglise>Management of Savings and Loan Association </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 32. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 32. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu &uuml;ldkoosoleku p&auml;devus </eesti>
<inglise>Competence of general meeting of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Lisaks tulundus&uuml;histuseaduses s&auml;testatule kuulub hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu &uuml;ldkoosoleku p&auml;devusse: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In addition to that provided for in the Commercial Associations Act, the general meeting of a savings and loan association is competent to: </inglise>
<eesti>(19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>(19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>1) majandusaasta eelarve kinnitamine; </eesti>
<inglise>1) approve the budget of the financial year; </inglise>
<eesti>2) (Kehtetu - 19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>2) (Repealed - 19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>3) liikmetele laenu andmise korra kehtestamine, sealhulgas &uuml;hele liikmele antava laenusumma piirm&auml;&auml;ra kehtestamine l&auml;htuvalt seadusest; </eesti>
<inglise>3) establish the procedure for granting loans to members, including the establishment, pursuant to law, of limits on the amount of loan granted to one member; </inglise>
<eesti>4) audiitori nimetamine, tema tasustamise aluste ja korra kehtestamine; </eesti>
<inglise>4) appoint an auditor and establish the bases and procedure for the remuneration of the auditor; </inglise>
<eesti>5) laenukomitee liikmete valimine ja tagasikutsumine enne volituste t&auml;htaja l&otilde;ppemist; </eesti>
<inglise>5) elect the members of the credit committee and remove them before the expiry of their term of authority; </inglise>
<eesti>6) (Kehtetu - 19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>6) (Repealed - 19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>7) laenukomitee tegevuse peale esitatud kaebuste l&auml;bivaatamine, kui hoiu-laenu&uuml;histus ei ole moodustatud n&otilde;ukogu; </eesti>
<inglise>7) hear the complaints filed against the activities of the credit committee, if the savings and loan association has not formed a supervisory board; </inglise>
<eesti>8) muude seaduse v&otilde;i p&otilde;hikirjaga &uuml;ldkoosoleku p&auml;devusse antud k&uuml;simuste otsustamine. </eesti>
<inglise>8) decide on other issues which are placed within the competence of the general meeting by law or the articles of association. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) (Kehtetu - 19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>(2) (Repealed - 19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 33. (Kehtetu - 19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 33. (Repealed - 19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 34. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 34. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatus </eesti>
<inglise>Management board of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Juhatuses on kolm liiget, kui p&otilde;hikiri ei n&auml;e ette suuremat liikmete arvu. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The management board shall consist of three members unless the articles of association prescribe a greater number of members. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Juhatuse liige ei pea olema hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu liige, kui p&otilde;hikirjaga ei ole ette n&auml;htud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Members of the management board are not required to be members of the savings and loan association unless otherwise prescribed by the articles of association. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) (Kehtetu - 19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>(3) (Repealed - 19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 35. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 35. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse esindus&otilde;igus </eesti>
<inglise>Right of representation of management board of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histut v&otilde;ivad esindada igas &otilde;igustoimingus koos v&auml;hemalt kaks juhatuse liiget, kui p&otilde;hikirjas ei ole ette n&auml;htud, et juhatuse liikmed esindavad hoiu-laenu&uuml;histut &uuml;hiselt. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A savings and loan association may be represented in all legal acts by at least two members of the management board together unless the articles of association prescribe that the members of the management board represent the savings and loan association jointly. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Juhatuse esindus&otilde;iguse piiramine ei kehti kolmandate isikute suhtes, kui see ei ole &auml;riregistrisse kantud. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Restriction of the right of representation of the management board does not apply to third parties unless the restriction is entered in the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 36. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 36. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse ja n&otilde;ukogu liikmetele esitatavad n&otilde;uded </eesti>
<inglise>Requirements for members of management board and supervisory board of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse ja n&otilde;ukogu liikmeks ei tohi olla pankrotiv&otilde;lgnik ega isik, kelle varasem tegevus v&otilde;i tegevusetus on p&otilde;hjustanud &auml;ri&uuml;hingu pankroti v&otilde;i sundlikvideerimise v&otilde;i tegevusloa t&uuml;histamise v&otilde;i kellelt on seaduse alusel &auml;ra v&otilde;etud &otilde;igus olla ettev&otilde;tja. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A bankrupt or a person whose earlier acts or omissions have caused the bankruptcy, compulsory liquidation or revocation of the activity licence of a company, or any other person from whom the right to engage in economic activity has been taken away pursuant to law shall not be a member of the management board or supervisory board of a savings and loan association. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse liikmeks v&otilde;ib olla teov&otilde;imeline f&uuml;&uuml;siline isik, kellel on laitmatu &auml;rialane reputatsioon, hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuses osalemiseks vajalik haridus, teadmised ja kutsealane sobivus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Natural persons with active legal capacity, impeccable business reputations and the education, experience and professional qualifications necessary for participation in the management board of a savings and loan association may be members of the management board of a savings and loan association. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse liige ei tohi olla hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu n&otilde;ukogu liige, hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu revisjonikomisjoni liige v&otilde;i hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu audiitor ega nendega samav&auml;&auml;rset majanduslikku huvi omav isik. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Members of the supervisory board or internal audit committee of a savings and loan association, the auditor of a savings and loan association and persons with economic interests equivalent to those of such persons shall not be members of the management board of a savings and loan association. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse liige ei v&otilde;i s&otilde;lmida teiste isikutega lepinguid, mille kohaselt on tema &uuml;lesandeks investeerimine, laenu- ja investeerimisprojektide koostamine v&otilde;i vahendamine v&otilde;i muu sarnane tegevus. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A member of the management board of a savings and loan association shall not enter into agreements with other persons if, pursuant to such agreements, the duties of the member include investment, the preparation or intermediation of loan or investment projects, or other similar activities. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse liige ei tohi olla krediidiasutuse ega teise hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse, n&otilde;ukogu, revisjonikomisjoni liige ega audiitor. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A member of the management board of a savings and loan association shall not be a member of the management board, supervisory board or internal audit committee, or the auditor of a credit institution or another savings and loan association. </inglise>
<eesti>7. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 7 </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu tegevuse kontrollimine </eesti>
<inglise>Monitoring of Activities of Savings and Loan Associations </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 37. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 37. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu revisjonikomisjon </eesti>
<inglise>Internal audit committee of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histul on kolmeliikmeline revisjonikomisjon, kui p&otilde;hikirjaga ei ole ette n&auml;htud suuremat liikmete arvu. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A savings and loan association shall have an internal audit committee which consists of three members unless a greater number of members is prescribed by the articles of association. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Revisjonikomisjoni liikmel peab olema majandusalane v&otilde;i juriidiline haridus v&otilde;i v&auml;hemalt kolmeaastane t&ouml;&ouml;kogemus raamatupidamise v&otilde;i rahanduse v&otilde;i &auml;ri&uuml;hingu majandustegevuse revideerimisega seotud ametikohal. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Members of the internal audit committee shall have education in economics or law or at least three years' work experience in a position related to accounting, finance or auditing of the economic activities of a company. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Revisjonikomisjoni liikmeks ei tohi olla hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatuse v&otilde;i n&otilde;ukogu ega laenukomitee liige, audiitor ega raamatupidaja ega nendega samav&auml;&auml;rset majanduslikku huvi omav isik. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Members of the management board, supervisory board or credit committee of a savings and loan association, auditors or accountants of savings and loan associations, and persons with economic interests equivalent to those of such persons shall not be members of the internal audit committee. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu majandustegevuse auditeerimine ei v&auml;lista revisjonikomisjoni tegevust. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) External auditing of the economic activities of a savings and loan association does not preclude the activities of the internal audit committee. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 38. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 38. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu revisjonikomisjoni &otilde;igused ja kohustused </eesti>
<inglise>Rights and obligations of internal audit committee of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Revisjonikomisjoni liikmel on &otilde;igus ja kohustus kontrollida hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu vara, arveldus- ja v&auml;&auml;rtpaberikontosid, raamatupidamisdokumente, laenukomitee tegevust kajastavaid dokumente ning &otilde;igus n&otilde;uda selgitusi ja k&otilde;ikv&otilde;imalikku abi oma &uuml;lesannete t&auml;itmiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Members of the internal audit committee have the right and obligation to verify the assets, bank accounts, securities accounts, accounting documents and documents relating to the activities of the credit committee of the savings and loan association, and the right to demand explanations and all possible assistance in the performance of their activities. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Revisjonikomisjoni liikmel on &otilde;igus j&auml;lgida hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu t&ouml;&ouml;d ja majandustegevust mis tahes l&otilde;igus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Members of the internal audit committee have the right to monitor any aspect of the work and economic activities of the savings and loan association. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 39. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 39. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu revisjonikomisjoni &uuml;lesanded </eesti>
<inglise>Duties of internal audit committee of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Revisjonikomisjon viib l&auml;bi &uuml;histu majandusaasta aruande revideerimise, koostab revisjoniaruande ja esitab selle &uuml;ldkoosolekule kinnitamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The internal audit committee shall audit the annual report of the association, prepare the internal audit report and submit the report to the general meeting for approval. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Revisjonikomisjon anal&uuml;&uuml;sib hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu t&ouml;&ouml;s ja majandustegevuses avastatud puudusi, koostab neist perioodilisi &uuml;levaateid ja esitab need olenevalt t&auml;htsuse astmest hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatusele, n&otilde;ukogule v&otilde;i &uuml;ldkoosolekule arutamiseks ja puuduste k&otilde;rvaldamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The internal audit committee shall analyse any deficiencies discovered in the work and economic activities of the savings and loan association, prepare reviews of the deficiencies on a regular basis and, depending on the degree of importance, submit the reviews to the management board, supervisory board or general meeting of the savings and loan association for hearing and for elimination of the deficiencies. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Revisjonikomisjon j&auml;lgib pidevalt hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu poolt k&auml;esoleva seaduse 5. peat&uuml;kis s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmist ja esitab vastava aruande &uuml;ldkoosolekule kinnitamiseks koos majandusaasta revisjoniaruandega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The internal audit committee shall continuously monitor compliance of the savings and loan association with the requirements provided for in Chapter 5 of this Act and submit a corresponding report to the general meeting for approval together with the annual internal audit report. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 40. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 40. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu revisjonikomisjoni tegevus hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu usaldusv&auml;&auml;rsuse tagamise n&otilde;uete rikkumise korral </eesti>
<inglise>Activities of internal audit committee of savings and loan association upon violation of requirements for guarantee of financial soundness of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu usaldusv&auml;&auml;rsuse tagamise meetmete ja laenudele esitatavate n&otilde;uete rikkumisest teatab revisjonikomisjon juhatusele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The internal audit committee shall notify the management board of violations of measures to guarantee the financial soundness of the savings and loan association and of violations of the requirements for loans. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu juhatus on kohustatud v&otilde;tma tarvitusele abin&otilde;ud rikkumiste k&otilde;rvaldamiseks kahe kuu jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The management board of a savings and loan association is required to take measures to eliminate violations within two months. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kui k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud t&auml;htaja jooksul rikkumisi ei k&otilde;rvaldata, kutsub revisjonikomisjon tulundus&uuml;histuseaduses m&auml;&auml;ratud korras kokku hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu erakorralise &uuml;ldkoosoleku. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) If violations are not eliminated during the term specified in subsection (2) of this section, the internal audit committee shall call a special general meeting of the savings and loan association pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Commercial Associations Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>(19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Revisjonikomisjon v&otilde;ib teha erakorralisele &uuml;ldkoosolekule ettepaneku: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The internal audit committee may make a proposal to a special general meeting to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) juhatuse v&otilde;i n&otilde;ukogu liikmete tagasikutsumiseks; </eesti>
<inglise>1) remove members of the management board or the supervisory board; </inglise>
<eesti>2) laenukomitee liikmete tagasikutsumiseks; </eesti>
<inglise>2) remove members of the credit committee; </inglise>
<eesti>3) p&otilde;hikirja muutmiseks; </eesti>
<inglise>3) amend the articles of association; </inglise>
<eesti>4) hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu &uuml;hinemiseks teise hoiu-laenu&uuml;histuga; </eesti>
<inglise>4) merge the savings and loan association with another savings and loan association; </inglise>
<eesti>5) hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu l&otilde;petamiseks seaduses ja p&otilde;hikirjas etten&auml;htud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>5) dissolve the savings and loan association pursuant to the procedure prescribed by law and the articles of association. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 41. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 41. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu audiitor </eesti>
<inglise>Auditor of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histul peab olema audiitor. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A savings and loan association shall have an auditor. </inglise>
