<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu jagunemine, &uuml;hinemine ja l&otilde;petamine </eesti>
<inglise>Division, Merger and Dissolution of Savings and Loan Associations </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 42. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 42. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu jagunemine ja &uuml;hinemine </eesti>
<inglise>Division and merger of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu jagunemine ei ole lubatud. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The division of a savings and loan association is prohibited. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu v&otilde;ib &uuml;hineda &uuml;ldkoosoleku otsuse alusel teise sama omavalitsus&uuml;ksuse haldusterritooriumil asuva v&otilde;i sellega piirneva omavalitsus&uuml;ksuse haldusterritooriumil asuva hoiu-laenu&uuml;histuga. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) On the basis of a resolution of the general meeting, a savings and loan association may merge with another savings and loan association located in the administrative territory of the same local government or in the administrative territory of a bordering local government. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histute &uuml;hinemine toimub &auml;riseadustikus etten&auml;htud korras, kui k&auml;esolevas seaduses ei ole ette n&auml;htud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The merger of savings and loan associations shall be effected pursuant to the procedure prescribed in the Commercial Code unless otherwise prescribed in this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 43. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 43. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hinemislepingu audiitorkontroll </eesti>
<inglise>Audit of merger agreement </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histute &uuml;hinemislepingut ja k&otilde;iki &uuml;hinevaid hoiu-laenu&uuml;histuid kontrollib &uuml;ks ja seesama audiitor. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A merger agreement between savings and loan associations, and all merging savings and loan associations shall be audited by one and the same auditor. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Audiitor koostab &uuml;hinemislepingu kontrollimise kohta aruande, n&auml;idates &auml;ra, milliseid hindamismeetodeid on kasutatud osamaksude vahetussuhte m&auml;&auml;ramisel, ja annab oma arvamuse usaldusv&auml;&auml;rsuse tagamise meetmete t&auml;itmise kohta &uuml;hinevates hoiu-laenu&uuml;histutes. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The auditor shall prepare a report concerning the audit of the merger agreement, indicate the assessment methods used to determine the exchange ratio of contributions, and give an opinion with regard to the compliance of the merging savings and loan associations with measures to guarantee financial soundness. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histute &uuml;hinemislepingut kontrollivad lisaks audiitorile ka &uuml;hinevate &uuml;histute revisjonikomisjonid ja koostavad kontrollimise kohta kirjaliku aruande. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In addition to the auditor, the audit committees of the merging savings and loan associations shall also audit the merger agreement of the associations and prepare a written report concerning the audit. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 44. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 44. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histute &uuml;hinemine &uuml;histupanga asutamiseks </eesti>
<inglise>Merger of savings and loan associations in order to found association bank </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histud v&otilde;ivad &uuml;hineda selliselt, et asutavad &uuml;histupanga vastavalt krediidiasutuste seaduse s&auml;tetele. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Savings and loan associations may merge in order to found an association bank pursuant to the provisions of the Credit Institutions Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hinevad hoiu-laenu&uuml;histud loetakse sel juhul l&otilde;ppenuks. </eesti>
<inglise>In such case, the merging savings and loan associations are deemed to be dissolved. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) &Uuml;histupanga asutamisel l&auml;heb &uuml;hinevate hoiu-laenu&uuml;histute vara &uuml;le asutatavale &uuml;histupangale ja hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu liikmetest saavad &uuml;histupanga liikmed. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Upon foundation of an association bank, the assets of the merging savings and loan associations transfer to the association bank being founded and the members of the savings and loan associations become members of the association bank. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 45. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 45. </inglise>
<eesti>Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu l&otilde;petamine </eesti>
<inglise>Dissolution of savings and loan association </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu l&otilde;petatakse: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A savings and loan association shall be dissolved: </inglise>
<eesti>1) &uuml;ldkoosoleku otsuse alusel; </eesti>
<inglise>1) on the basis of a resolution of the general meeting; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kohtuotsusega; </eesti>
<inglise>2) by a court judgment; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kui hoiu-laenu&uuml;histusse on j&auml;&auml;nud v&auml;hem kui 25 liiget ja liikmete arv ei ole kahe kuu jooksul suurenenud; </eesti>
<inglise>3) if the savings and loan association has less than twenty-five members and the number of members has not increased during two months; </inglise>
<eesti>4) muudel seaduse v&otilde;i p&otilde;hikirjaga s&auml;testatud alustel. </eesti>
<inglise>4) on other bases provided by law or the articles of association. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu l&otilde;petamine toimub tulundus&uuml;histuseaduses etten&auml;htud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A savings and loan association shall be dissolved pursuant to the procedure prescribed in the Commercial Associations Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(19.12.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </eesti>
<inglise>(19.12.2001 entered into force 01.02.2002 - RT I 2002, 3, 6) </inglise>
<eesti>9. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 9 </inglise>
<eesti>Rakenduss&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>Implementing Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 46. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 46. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse kohaldamine asutatavatele ja tegutsevatele hoiu-laenu&uuml;histutele </eesti>
<inglise>Application of Act to savings and loan associations being founded or operating </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Alates k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest saab hoiu-laenu&uuml;histuid asutada ainult k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud korras ja neile hoiu-laenu&uuml;histutele kohaldatakse k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatut. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) As of the entry into force of this Act, savings and loan associations shall be founded only pursuant to the procedure provided for in this Act and the provisions of this Act apply to such savings and loan associations. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisel tegutsevad laenu-hoiu&uuml;histud loetakse hoiu-laenu&uuml;histuteks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Loan and savings associations operating upon the entry into force of this Act are deemed to be savings and loan associations. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kolme kuu jooksul, arvates k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest, peavad j&otilde;ustumise hetkel tegutsevad hoiu-laenu&uuml;histud viima oma tegevuse ja dokumendid vastavusse k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Savings and loan associations operating upon the entry into force of this Act shall bring their activities and documents into conformity with the requirements of this Act within three months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 47. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 47. </inglise>
<eesti>Osakapitalile s&auml;testatud n&otilde;ude rakendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Application of requirements provided for share capital </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Alates k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest peab hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu osakapital olema v&auml;hemalt 200 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) As of the entry into force of this Act, the share capital of a savings and loan association shall be at least 200 000 kroons. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Alates 2001. aasta 1. juulist peab hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu osakapital olema v&auml;hemalt 300 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) As of 1 July 2001, the share capital of a savings and loan association shall be at least 300 000 kroons. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Alates 2002. aasta 1. juulist peab hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu osakapital vastama k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 22 l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatule. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) As of 1 July 2002, the share capital of a savings and loan association shall comply with the provisions of subsection 22 (3) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu ei vii oma osakapitali suurust vastavusse k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1-3 s&auml;testatuga, kustutab registripidaja hoiu-laenu&uuml;histu registrist v&otilde;i algatab selle sundl&otilde;petamise &auml;riseadustiku &sect;-s 60 s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If a savings and loan association fails to bring the amount of share capital of the association into conformity with the provisions of subsections (1) -(3) of this section, the registrar shall delete the savings and loan association from the register or commence compulsory dissolution of the association pursuant to the procedure provided for in &sect; 60 of the Commercial Code. </inglise>
